quran[7]{c,v,t,f}:
  36,1,"Yâ-Sîn."
  36,2,"By the Qur’ân, full of wisdom (i.e. full of laws, evidence, and proofs),"
  36,3,"Truly, you (O Muhammad صلى الله عليه وسلم) are one of the Messengers,"
  36,4,"On the Straight Path (i.e. on Allâh’s religion of Islâmic Monotheism)."
  36,5,"(This is a Revelation) sent down by the All-Mighty, the Most Merciful,"
  36,6,"In order that you may warn a people whose forefathers were not warned, so they are heedless."
  36,7,"Indeed the Word (of punishment) has proved true against most of them, so they will not believe."
  36,8,"Verily We have put on their necks iron collars reaching to the chins, so that their heads are raised up."
  36,9,"And We have put a barrier before them, and a barrier behind them, and We have covered them up, so that they cannot see."
  36,10,"It is the same to them whether you warn them or you warn them not, they will not believe."